SHRI SUNIL SIDDHARTHBHAI V. COMMISSIONER OF INCOME TAX, AHMEDABAD [1985] INSC 208; AIR 1986 SC 368; 1985 (3) Suppl.SCR 102; 1985 (4) SCC 519; 1985 (2) SCALE 755 (27 September 1985)

 PATHAK, R.S.
